      },
      "source": [
        "5. What are recursive functions, and how are they used?\n",
        "\n",
        "Functions that call itself are called recursive functions.\n",
        "\n",
        "def func():\n",
        "  if base condition:\n",
        "    return\n",
        "  return func()"
      ]
